{"tid":1238353,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我地贏撚晒啦","createTime":"2019-06-17T19:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T03:02:41.000Z","uid":137831,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"81c633fda29c15e36237a88d23ba0d6d245491f2","tid":1238353,"uid":137831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T19:16:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我贏你條撚呀<br />\n撤回修例<br />\n暫緩<br />\n林鄭下台<br />\n柒婆:我仲有好撚多嘢未做<br />\n撤回定性暴動<br />\n狗長:五人暴動<br />\n林鄭道歉<br />\n書面致歉<br />\n我哋贏撚咗啲咩？<br />\n政府當我地傻閪呀<br />\n如果唔係外國傳媒？<br />\n條修例一早過撚左啦<br />\n<br />\n我話撚定比你地聽<br />\n就算有一個人比狗告暴動都唔得！<br />\n到時邊個割席就割撚！<br />\n唔好因為上咗幾日外國頭條就喺度打飛機<br />\n政府再唔係20號之前達成訴求<br />\n就要即刻冚家齊人去做野<br />\n<br />\n歷史同我地講冇一個腐敗政權係推翻唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Pb4ANX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Pb4ANX.png&h=d6209ddf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港人係呢個時候咪撚再善忘啦我屌你老母臭閪<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"5febbbc8ecacc8c9ecc90b68c980a2206179610e","tid":1238353,"uid":14479,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T19:20:13.000Z","msg":"諗住屌柒你我先㩒入嚟"},{"pid":"efcb7b2259593375c9b1455af9f63fe9ca31c522","tid":1238353,"uid":98520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5febbbc8ecacc8c9ecc90b68c980a2206179610e","tid":1238353,"uid":14479,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T19:20:13.000Z","msg":"諗住屌柒你我先㩒入嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T19:21:32.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053f45a55a985c41746138e7b5b255c761435cf1","tid":1238353,"uid":258234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5febbbc8ecacc8c9ecc90b68c980a2206179610e","tid":1238353,"uid":14479,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T19:20:13.000Z","msg":"諗住屌柒你我